        GEOoptimised audits your content against every stage of the generative pipeline and delivers a prioritised remediation plan. Our <a href="/geo-services/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">GEO services</a> cover audit, entity authority building, content restructuring, schema implementation, and ongoing citation monitoring.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
